#### Dependency license analysis: `liccheck`
Liccheck is configured in the `[tools.liccheck]` section of the `pyproject.toml` file.

```
liccheck
```

e.g.
```bash
$ liccheck
gathering licenses...
8 packages and dependencies.
check authorized packages...
8 packages.
```
